<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="flight-n">flight <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /flaɪt/    美 /flaɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 飞翔；飞行：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a bird <strong>in flight</strong>
飞行中的鸟</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Flight is natural to birds. 
飞翔是鸟类的天性。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] 班机；航班；空中旅行：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>book / catch / miss a flight</strong>
预订航班/赶上飞机/误机</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>a long / short flight</strong> 
长途/短途飞行</p></div>

<h4 id="3u">3.<strong>[U] 逃跑；逃避：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When the alarm sounded, the robbers <strong>took flight</strong> in a hurry.
警报声响起，劫匪匆忙逃跑。</p></div>

<h4 id="4c">4.<strong>[C] (楼梯等的) 一段：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>a flight of stairs / steps</strong>
一段楼梯/台阶</p></div></div>